30:09.183 --> 30:10.601
Next?

30:10.601 --> 30:13.354
Hey, I didn't know you worked
at the derby.

30:13.354 --> 30:15.648
Just filling in for...

30:15.648 --> 30:17.024
Diggins.

30:18.609 --> 30:22.655
So, pay attention
